   <topic>FILE.DIR_PUT Function</topic>
 <description>The FILE.DIR_PUT() method changes the current location to the specified directory.</description>  
   <syntax>V Dir_Put(C directory)</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>directory</name>
         <description>The path and name of the new directory</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>

   <example><![CDATA[
file.dir_put("c:\temp")
? file.dir_get()
= "C:\TEMP"   
]]></example>
 
